# 📚 Design Patterns Covered

## Creational Design Patterns

| Pattern | Purpose |
|----------|----------|
| Singleton | Ensure only one object exists |
| Factory Method | Create objects without exposing creation logic |
| Builder | Construct complex objects step-by-step |

---

## Structural Design Patterns

| Pattern | Purpose |
|----------|----------|
| Adapter | Connect incompatible interfaces |
| Decorator | Add functionality dynamically |

---

## Behavioral Design Patterns

| Pattern | Purpose |
|----------|----------|
| Observer | Notify multiple objects automatically |
| Strategy | Select algorithms at runtime |
| Command | Encapsulate requests as objects |

