# ⚙ Prerequisites

Before running the projects, ensure the following software is installed.

- .NET 8 SDK
- Visual Studio 2022 or Visual Studio Code
- Git
- GitHub Account

Verify installation

```bash
dotnet --version
```

Expected Output

```text
8.x.x
```

---

# 🚀 How to Run the Projects

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/Cognizant_Deep_Skilling.git
```

Move into the repository

```bash
cd WEEK-1
```

Navigate to any project

```bash
cd SingletonPattern
```

Run the project

```bash
dotnet run
```

